{"article_id":"KKDg2Tw4egV3A9VR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Top White House adviser Kellyanne Conway said Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that a judge ' s ruling","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to force former White House Counsel Don McGahn to testify in the House impeachment inquiry","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"\" may not be sustainable . \"","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Mrs. Conway told reporters at the White House","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that \" nobody was surprised \" by the ruling Monday from U.S. District Judge Ketanji Brown Jackson ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and that the Justice Department will appeal .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"\" This is one judge , an Obama-appointed judge , \"","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"she said ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that the ruling \" may not be sustainable . \"","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The judge decided","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that Mr. McGahn must testify in the House impeachment investigation ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"undercutting an order from President Trump","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"blocking his cooperation with Congress .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The ruling said","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that ignoring a congressional subpoena is \" an affront to the mechanism","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"for curbing abuses","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that the framers carefully crafted for our protection . \"","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"The president had invoked \" absolute immunity \"","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"to shield witnesses from testifying in the Democrats ' impeachment probe .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Mr. Trump said on Twitter Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"that he would \" love \" to have Mr. McGahn and other high-ranking administration officials testify ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"but he ' s \" fighting for future Presidents and the Office of the President . \"","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"\" Future Presidents should in no way be compromised , \"","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"\" What has happened to me should never happen to another President ! \"","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"his critics \" are reading far too much into people","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"being forced by Courts to testify before Congress . \"","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"\" I would actually like people to testify .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Don McGahn","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"[ is a ]","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"respected lawyer","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"has already stated","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that I did nothing wrong , \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"\" Likewise , I would love to have Mike Pompeo , Rick Perry , Mick Mulvaney and many others testify about the phony Impeachment Hoax .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"It is a Democrat Scam","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that is going nowhere... \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"The ruling also could pave the way for other impeachment witnesses","depth":3},{"id":41,"text":"who have sought to duck congressional investigators .","depth":3},{"id":42,"text":"One potential key witness , former National Security Adviser John R. Bolton , said","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"he would not testify","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"unless a court ordered him to do so .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"The president said in an apparent message to Mr. Bolton ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"\" John Bolton is a patriot","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"and may know","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that I held back the money from Ukraine","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"because it is considered a corrupt country ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"& I wanted to know","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"why nearby European countries weren ' t putting up money also . \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Mr. Bolton tweeted later in the day ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"\" It probably goes without saying , that our country ' s commitment to our national security priorities is under attack from within .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"America is distracted .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Our enemies are not .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"We need to make U.S. national security a priority . \"","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo ,","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"asked by a reporter Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"if he would testify in the impeachment inquiry ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"replied ,","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"\" When the time is right ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"all good things happen . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":125,"left":102,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":83,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":73,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":66,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":0,"right":65,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":65,"left":64,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":68,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":4,"right":67,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":69,"right":70,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":69,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":82,"left":80,"right":81,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":76,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":74,"right":75,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","n